{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WM9xB5eKnWggwcxuNV9L1b","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tstepsCompleted: [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]\n3\tstatus: complete\n4\tdate: '2026-04-03'\n5\tproject_name: 'codeharness'\n6\tdocuments:\n7\t  prd: 'prd.md'\n8\t  architecture: 'architecture-multi-framework.md'\n9\t  epics: null\n10\t  ux: null\n11\t---\n12\t\n13\t# Implementation Readiness Assessment Report\n14\t\n15\t**Date:** 2026-04-03\n16\t**Project:** codeharness (Multi-Framework Orchestration)\n17\t\n18\t## Document Inventory\n19\t\n20\t| Document | File | Status |\n21\t|----------|------|--------|\n22\t| PRD | prd.md | Active ✓ |\n23\t| PRD Validation | prd-validation-report.md | Pass (4.5/5) ✓ |\n24\t| Architecture | architecture-multi-framework.md | Active ✓ |\n25\t| Epics & Stories | — | Not yet created |\n26\t| UX Design | — | Not updated for multi-framework |\n27\t\n28\t## PRD Analysis\n29\t\n30\t### Functional Requirements (38 FRs)\n31\t\n32\t| Area | FRs | Count |\n33\t|------|-----|-------|\n34\t| Driver Management | FR1-FR6 | 6 |\n35\t| Stream Event Normalization | FR7-FR10 | 4 |\n36\t| Workflow Configuration | FR11-FR15 | 5 |\n37\t| Cross-Framework Task Execution | FR16-FR20 | 5 |\n38\t| Plugin Ecosystem Integration | FR21-FR23 | 3 |\n39\t| TUI Workflow Visualization | FR24-FR30 | 7 |\n40\t| TUI Activity Display Extension | FR31-FR33 | 3 |\n41\t| Cost Tracking & Routing | FR34-FR36 | 3 |\n42\t| Driver Capability Matrix | FR37-FR38 | 2 |\n43\t\n44\t### Non-Functional Requirements (18 NFRs)\n45\t\n46\t| Category | NFRs | Count |\n47\t|----------|------|-------|\n48\t| Performance | NFR1-NFR6 | 6 |\n49\t| Integration | NFR7-NFR12 | 6 |\n50\t| Reliability | NFR13-NFR18 | 6 |\n51\t\n52\t### PRD Completeness Assessment\n53\t\n54\t- **FR quality:** All 38 FRs follow \"[Actor] can [capability]\" format. PRD validation scored 4.5/5.\n55\t- **NFR quality:** All 18 NFRs have measurable criteria. 3 minor template gaps flagged in validation.\n56\t- **Scope clarity:** MVP scope explicitly defined with 15 must-have capabilities. Post-MVP clearly separated.\n57\t- **Out of scope:** 4 items explicitly excluded (dynamic routing, parallel execution, marketplace, workflow composition).\n58\t- **Traceability:** All FRs trace to user journeys. No orphan requirements.\n59\t- **Assessment:** PRD is complete and ready for epic breakdown.\n60\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01UsAm2qXT84D1u4sW8gSAmJ","session_id":"a29ee53b-c2b0-4802-9455-7215112648b1","uuid":"8efdf3c1-25f2-44fa-8cea-064f1c3baa01","timestamp":"2026-04-03T11:57:40.223Z"}
