 7, Bash: 3, Glob: 4, Write: 1, Edit: 1). 12 unique files. No redundancy.\n\n### 13-2-output-contract-prompt-injection — dev-story (2026-04-03T10:27)\n\n- **`previousOutputContract` parameter never called yet.** Story 13-3 will supply the actual contract from `readOutputContract()`. By design.\n- **No workflow-engine integration test for wiring.** Existing test infrastructure uses heavy mocking; unit tests on formatting functions cover the logic.\n\nToken Report: 13 tool calls (Read: 5, Edit: 9, Bash: 3, Grep: 1). 5 unique files. No redundancy.\n\n### 13-2-output-contract-prompt-injection — code-review (2026-04-03T10:32)\n\n- **MEDIUM: `dispatchTask()` public API missing `previousOutputContract` parameter.** The internal `dispatchTaskWithResult()` accepted the parameter, but the public `dispatchTask()` didn't forward it, making the wiring dead code for story 13-3. Fixed.\n- **MEDIUM: No workflow engine integration test for contract injection (AC #10).** Fixed by adding vi.mock and 2 integration tests.\n- **MEDIUM: Missing boundary test for output truncation at exactly 2001 characters.** Fixed.\n- **LOW (not fixed): No markdown sanitization in `formatContractAsPromptContext`.** By design.\n- **LOW (not fixed): `toFixed(2)` cost formatting shows `$0.00` for sub-cent costs.** Cosmetic.\n- Coverage: 96.8% overall, all 170 files above 80% floor.\n\nToken Report: 25 tool calls (Bash: 7, Read: 10, Edit: 6, Grep: 5, Glob: 2). workflow-engine.test.ts read 3x.\n\n### 13-2-output-contract-prompt-injection — verify (2026-04-03T10:38)\n\n- **Lint error:** 1 pre-existing `require-yield` error in unrelated file — not from story 13-2.\n- **Verify format mismatch:** Initial proof used wrong format (`**Status:** PASS` instead of `**Verdict:** PASS`). Rewrote to match expected format.\n- **Verify warnings:** No exec-plan found and Showboat not installed — non-blocking.\n- ALL_PASS: 12/12 ACs verified.\n\nToken Report: 14 tool calls (Bash: 8, Read: 2, Grep: 4, Write: 1). 2 unique files