s-framework-workflow-execution — verify (2026-04-03T11:10)\n\n- **Proof format mismatch:** Proof had `**Verification tier:**` but parser expects `**Tier:**`. Fixed.\n- **Pre-existing lint error:** `require-yield` at workflow-engine.test.ts:164 — generator function from 13-3 tests, not a regression.\n- **Verification gap:** AC 7 (crash recovery + contract persistence) verified by code inspection rather than a dedicated combined test.\n- **Coverage not run by verifier** — `codeharness coverage` not invoked. Test count (4545) and prior code-review coverage (96.82%) provide confidence.\n- ALL_PASS: 10/10 ACs verified. `codeharness verify` passes (exit 0).\n\nToken Report: 17 tool calls (Bash: 9, Read: 4, Grep: 5, Write: 1). 4 unique files. `npm run lint` checked twice, `ls verification/` run twice (minor redundancy).\n\nToken Report: 27 tool calls (Bash: 8, Read: 16, Edit: 3, Grep: 5, Glob: 1, Skill: 1). 8 unique files. workflow-engine.test.ts read 8x (size-limited).\n\n---\n\n# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03 (Session 10)\n\n### 14-1-workflowgraph-component — create-story (2026-04-03T11:14)\n\n- **No UX spec coverage for workflow graph.** UX design spec predates multi-framework PRD. All behavioral requirements from epics/architecture only.\n- **Spinner vs static indicator:** Architecture says \"cyan + spinner\" for active tasks, but codebase uses `◆`. Defaulted to `◆`, deferred spinner to 14-2.\n- **ink-testing-library availability unknown.** Dev notes instruct developer to check before writing tests.\n- **Sprint-status not updated by subagent** — orchestrator handled it.\n\nToken Report: 18 tool calls (Bash: 3, Read: 10, Glob: 5, Grep: 2, Write: 1, Skill: 1). 12 unique files, 14 total reads. ink-components.tsx and ink-renderer.tsx read 2x each.\n\n### 14-1-workflowgraph-component — dev-story (2026-04-03T11:18)\n\n- **Loop iteration counting is a heuristic.** `loopIteration()` returns 0 or 1 — real iteration count requires engine-provided data wired in integration stor