ty-display-driver-integration — code-review (2026-04-03T12:14)\n\n- **HIGH: Renderer driver tests had zero expect() assertions** — only verified no exceptions. Replaced with 6 App-level rendering tests with real assertions.\n- **HIGH: No test for DriverCostSummary in App layout.** Added App-level integration tests.\n- **MEDIUM: No test for driver name surviving args truncation (60-char limit).** Fixed.\n- **LOW (not fixed): Redundant two-stage null guard** in DriverCostSummary.\n- **Architecture: update() driverName not connected to workflow engine** — inert in production until future integration story.\n- Coverage: 96.86% overall, all 171 files above 80% floor. 4598 tests pass.\n\nToken Report: 19 tool calls (Bash: 6, Read: 10, Edit: 3, Grep: 4, Glob: 1, Skill: 1). 11 unique files, 12 total reads. No redundancy.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":289,"oldLines":3,"newStart":289,"newLines":13,"lines":[" - Coverage: 96.86% overall, all 171 files above 80% floor. 4598 tests pass."," "," Token Report: 19 tool calls (Bash: 6, Read: 10, Edit: 3, Grep: 4, Glob: 1, Skill: 1). 11 unique files, 12 total reads. No redundancy.","+","+### 14-3-activity-display-driver-integration — verify (2026-04-03T12:18)","+","+- **Verification format mismatch:** First proof attempt used table format; rewrote to `## AC N:` + `**Verdict:**` format. Known issue.","+- **Warnings:** `No exec-plan found` and `Showboat not installed` — non-blocking.","+- **Pre-existing lint error:** 1 in `src/templates/otel-config.ts`, not from story.","+- **Verification gap:** AC 4 (multi-driver correctness) verified via unit tests only, no integration test with real multi-driver workflow.","+- ALL_PASS: 12/12 ACs verified.","+","+Token Report: 14 tool calls (Bash: 9, Read: 2, Grep: 5, Write: 2). 2 unique files. `codeharness verify` run twice (format fix cycle)."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
