{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013d31iE1J8aMmVuKLf8w7LN","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Harness Cost Report\n2\t\n3\tTotal API-equivalent cost: $250.40\n4\tTotal API calls: 1936\n5\tAverage cost per story: $3.41 (62 stories)\n6\t\n7\t## Cost by Token Type\n8\t\n9\t| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n10\t|------|--------|------|------|---|\n11\t| Cache reads | 103,033,999 | $1.50/MTok | $154.55 | 62% |\n12\t| Cache writes | 2,928,732 | $18.75/MTok | $54.91 | 22% |\n13\t| Output | 544,575 | $75/MTok | $40.84 | 16% |\n14\t| Input | 6,022 | $15/MTok | $0.09 | 0% |\n15\t\n16\t## Cost by Phase\n17\t\n18\t| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n19\t|-------|-------|------|---|\n20\t| verify | 947 | $113.94 | 45.5% |\n21\t| orchestrator | 214 | $44.84 | 17.9% |\n22\t| create-story | 235 | $26.87 | 10.7% |\n23\t| dev-story | 234 | $26.16 | 10.4% |\n24\t| code-review | 184 | $21.80 | 8.7% |\n25\t| retro | 122 | $16.78 | 6.7% |\n26\t\n27\t## Cost by Tool\n28\t\n29\t| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n30\t|------|-------|------|---|\n31\t| Bash | 609 | $67.30 | 26.9% |\n32\t| Read | 428 | $58.67 | 23.4% |\n33\t| Edit | 385 | $47.65 | 19.0% |\n34\t| Agent | 247 | $36.01 | 14.4% |\n35\t| Skill | 44 | $15.70 | 6.3% |\n36\t| Grep | 120 | $12.86 | 5.1% |\n37\t| Write | 40 | $5.16 | 2.1% |\n38\t| Glob | 43 | $4.61 | 1.8% |\n39\t| TodoWrite | 17 | $2.20 | 0.9% |\n40\t| ToolSearch | 3 | $0.25 | 0.1% |\n41\t\n42\t## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n43\t\n44\t| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n45\t|-------|-------|------|---|\n46\t| unknown | 159 | $39.22 | 15.7% |\n47\t| 5-1-flow-execution-sequential-steps | 65 | $8.84 | 3.5% |\n48\t| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | 69 | $8.51 | 3.4% |\n49\t| 9-2-custom-workflow-creation | 64 | $6.83 | 2.7% |\n50\t| 3-2-embedded-agent-templates | 49 | $6.42 | 2.6% |\n51\t| 6-2-evaluator-verdict-json-schema-parsing | 45 | $6.15 | 2.5% |\n52\t| 5-4-run-status-commands | 55 | $6.14 | 2.5% |\n53\t| 9-1-workflow-patch-resolution | 53